headline: Planet 13 Continues Florida Expansion, Opening its New Pace Dispensary on a Busy Retail Corridor near Pensacola
summary: Las Vegas, NV, Oct. 20, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- – Planet 13 Holdings Inc. (CSE: PLTH) (OTCQX: PLNH) (“Planet 13” or the “Company”), a leading vertically-integrated multi-state cannabis company, today announced the opening of its newest Florida dispensary in Pace at 4612 School Lane just off busy US Highway 90. Located along a bustling retail corridor directly across from a Walmart and Lowe’s, Planet 13 Pace will be open Monday through Saturday from 9 a.m. to 7 p.m. and from 11 a.m. to 5 p.m. on
